commits.message:
Adding Memorable Date Component (#879)

* consolidating preview methods

* erb linting

* addressing some failing checks

* fix for random pdf text content issue that popped up due to line breaks in the pdf. restored applicant_informations_controller

* moved the require pdf-reader to the top of the test_helpers

* addressing pr feedback

* changing date to be multi-parameter, removing mutex_m gem- will add in follow up pr

* changing label -> legend for memorable date component

* updated the date_of_birth help text to match that of USWDS - For example: January 19 2000

* normalized locales
commits.author: George Byers II

commits.message:
FFS-3220: Use most recent source for origin tracking (#885)

Origin tracking used to keep the first received origin and persist it throughout the session, rejecting any subsequent origins. This was found to be unacceptable for go-live, and now we will update the origin any time we receive a different one.
commits.author: Tim Miller
